import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Planet from '../../orbitStories/Planet'
import { Record } from '../../src/Record'
import Display from './Display'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"record"}}>{`Record`}</MDXTag>

<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"basic-usage"}}>{`Basic usage`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={0} __code={`<Planet id="earth">{({ planet }) => <Display object={planet} />}</Planet>`} __scope={{props,Planet,Record,Display}}>
  <Planet id='earth'>
    {({ planet }) => <Display object={planet}/>}
  </Planet>
</Playground>
<PropsTable of={Record} /></MDXTag>
